<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>ServiceWatch</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                background-color: #F5F5F5;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            a {
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .navbar {
                background-color: #131a26;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 10px 0;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                position: fixed;
                width: 100%;
                top: 0;
            }

            .navbar-logo {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .logo-img {
                margin-left: 0.2em;
                width: 40%;
            }

            .btn-login {
                background-color: #3bd671;
                color: #fff;
                border: none;
                border-radius: 2em;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1em;
                cursor: pointer;
                font-weight:700;
                margin-right: 1em;
            }

            .container {
                text-align: center;
                margin: 70px 20px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                color: #131a26;
            }

            .footer {
                background-color: #131a26;
                color: #fff;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 10px 0;
                position:fixed;
                bottom:0;
                width: 100%;
                font-weight: 600;
                display:flex;
                flex-direction:row;
                justify-content:end;
            }

            .div-texto {
                width: 50%;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .div-componente {
                display: flex;
                padding: 2em;
                height: 70vh;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-logo">
                <img class="logo-img" src="logo.png" alt="Logo">
            </div>
            <a class="btn-login" href="login">Iniciar Sesión</a>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
        <div class="div-componente">
            <div class="div-texto">
                <h1>Todos los servicios que te interesan
                    <span style="color: #3bd671 !important;">monitoreados</span> en un solo lugar<span style="color: #3bd671 !important;">.</span></h1>
                <a class="btn-login" href="login">Comenzar</a>
            </div>
            <div style="width: 50%;">
                <img src="landing_imagen.svg" style="height: 65vh;"></img>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div style="margin-right: 0.5em;">ServiceWatch © 2023</div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>